OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 12 MAR
OL,4,CEVENTS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1961FKenneth Kendall left the BBC TV
OL,7,Fnewsreading team, reportedly to go on
OL,8,Fattachment to the BBC TV Planning
OL,9,FDepartment. He would return to
OL,10,Fnewsreading duties on 14th July 1969,
OL,11,Fafter eight years of TV presenting in
OL,12,Fother genres.
