OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 12 MAR
OL,4,CEVENTS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1999FBroadcast magazine reports that
OL,7,FMoira Stuart is to present BBC
OL,8,FBreakfast News when it relaunches in
OL,9,Fthe autumn: "The format is yet to be
OL,10,Fconfirmed, although the BBC is believed
OL,11,Fto be considering the inclusion of news
OL,12,Fbulletins within the show." In fact,
OL,13,Fthe relaunched version of the programme
OL,14,Fdidn't materialise until October 2000.
OL,15,FMoira joined at that point, presenting
OL,16,Fnews bulletins.
